  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/be7eeb4305a72822372fc83f01210bb7.poster.avif?t=1732819897\" width=610 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/be7eeb4305a72822372fc83f01210bb7.webm?t=1732819897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/be7eeb4305a72822372fc83f01210bb7.mp4?t=1732819897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Papelina wants to find the Origami Treasure, with the guidance of the treasure map, our adventurer travels to Folding Island.<br>She goes through different scenarios with unique obstacles and enemies, folds into various origami to adapt to the difficulties of the journey. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/49c9dd2b0a545b9b96b2a3b59403ddf0.poster.avif?t=1732819897\" width=610 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/49c9dd2b0a545b9b96b2a3b59403ddf0.webm?t=1732819897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/49c9dd2b0a545b9b96b2a3b59403ddf0.mp4?t=1732819897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>With Papelita, explore Folding Island in this beautiful 2D platform.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fold into a paper plane, paper boat or paper frog to adapt to obstacles.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 weather vanes in each level to collect.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel across 4 worlds with a total of 32 stages.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defeat 4 bosses to find the Origami Treasure.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support for Xbox and DualShock controllers.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Steam Achievements.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/19f6fe692aea71f005ff51e53d31086f.poster.avif?t=1732819897\" width=610 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/19f6fe692aea71f005ff51e53d31086f.webm?t=1732819897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820580/extras/19f6fe692aea71f005ff51e53d31086f.mp4?t=1732819897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you to find the Origami Treasure?",
